==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Devoir
<hw>De*voir"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., fr. L.
<ets>debere</ets> to owe. See <er>Due</er>.]</ety> <def>Duty; service
owed; hence, due act of civility or respect; -- now usually in the
plural; <as>as, they paid their <ex>devoirs</ex> to the
ladies</as>.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧Do now your <xex>devoid</xex>, young
knights!⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Devolute</ent>⟦br⟧
